# Cursor Rules for personal-background

This is the user's personal background repository. It contains a unified, local-first, markdown-based knowledge base at `~/Documents/workspace/personal-background/`.

When helping this user, reference:

- `profile.md` — stable identity: education, work, skills, goals, projects
- `preferences.md` — decision preferences: risk tolerance, values, communication style
- `constraints.md` — hard constraints: geography, budget, time, family, health, technology
- `episodes/` — timestamped experiences
- `notes/` — free observations and distilled preferences

Respect privacy boundaries. Never upload or reference files in `raw/private/` unless explicitly asked.
